### Appointment API

### Get all appointments (paginated)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/appointments?page=0&size=20

### Get appointment by ID
GET {{host}}/api/v1/appointments/{{appointmentId}}

### Create appointment
POST {{host}}/api/v1/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "petId": "{{petId}}",
  "vetId": "{{vetId}}",
  "scheduledAt": "2025-02-01T10:00:00Z",
  "reason": "Annual checkup"
}

### Update appointment
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/appointments/{{appointmentId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scheduledAt": "2025-02-05T14:00:00Z",
  "reason": "Rescheduled - vaccination"
}

### Confirm appointment
POST {{host}}/api/v1/appointments/{{appointmentId}}/confirm

### Cancel appointment
POST {{host}}/api/v1/appointments/{{appointmentId}}/cancel

### Complete appointment (creates visit)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/appointments/{{appointmentId}}/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "diagnosis": "Healthy, no issues found",
  "treatment": "Routine vaccination administered"
}

### Send reminder notification
POST {{host}}/api/v1/appointments/{{appointmentId}}/notify
